data.description: This adorable home captures the San Diego Lifestyle with a panoramic ocean view from the 696 sq.ft. Ipe wood deck, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms and built on a 6800 sq.ft. lot and recently had the windows replaced through the SD Quieter Homes Program and offers an abundance of privacy, peace and a tranquil setting. Terrific natural light in each room and  cool ocean breezes year round. Also featured, is the Primary or Guest room with ensuite full bathroom. Excellent home to make your own!
